<h2 id="add-more-css">Add more CSS</h2>

<p>Paste the following in to the <em>main.css</em> file, replacing your <code class="highlighter-rouge">h1</code> definition and all the current contents of the file. If you have trouble copying it, there‚Äôs a raw text version of the whole file <a href="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/GeneralProducts/publisher-website/finished-example/assets/css/main.css">here</a>.</p>

